Revision history for Task-BeLike-HMA-Toolchain

0.07_01 Jul 25, 2011

        - Add optional modules for enhancement of CPAN.pm
            * Archive::Zip
            * CPAN::Meta
            * JSON::PP
            * Module::CoreList
            * Parse::CPAN::Meta
        - Remove YAML::Tiny

0.07    Jul 23, 2011

        - FIX: Updating Pod::Man requires Pod::Usage to be updated too
        - Don't install CPAN::SQLite under perlbrewed Perls
        - Latest YAML::XS (0.35) available again on Perl 5.8.5
        - Convert README to Markdown
        - Upgrade to Module::Install 1.01

0.06    Jul 15, 2011

        - Require Perl::OSType and Module::Metadata for Module::Build 0.36_20+
        - Require Scalar::Util 1.18 for YAML::Tiny 1.48+

0.05    Jan 15, 2011

        - Add optional modules for enhancement of CPAN.pm
            * CPAN::SQLite
            * DBD::SQLite
            * DBI
        - Make more dependencies explicit which latest versions fail
          on legacy Perls
            * HTML::Parser
            * Pod::Simple
            * URI
        - Require Scalar::Util 1.08 to workaround a bug in YAML::Tiny
          (RT #53490)
        - Bump YAML::XS to 0.34 and make its installation dependent on
          Perl 5.8.8 (RT #62054)
        - Don't install YAML::Syck if YAML::XS can be installed
        - Disable Encode, File::HomeDir, File::Which, IO::File on 5.6.x
        - Disable Storable, YAML::Syck on 5.8.0
        - Switch GitHub URLs to https

0.03    Oct 10, 2010

        - Made more dependencies explicit for ease of individual update
            * Compress::Zlib
            * Digest::MD5
            * ExtUtils::Manifest
            * File::Path
            * File::Spec
            * Net::FTP
            * Test
            * version.pm
        - Added optional modules for enhancement of CPAN.pm
            * File::HomeDir
            * File::Which
            * Storable
            * Text::Glob
        - Bumped to more recent versions
            * Module::Build and dependencies
            * Test::More
        - Added YAML::Syck for YAML support in very legacy Perls
        - Changed minimum Perl version to 5.6.1

0.01    Sep 11, 2010

        - Initial commit and release to GitHub
